e3a4b21b27f381659b9997bb: SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime FROM diagnoses_icd JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 <= 3 )

SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title 
FROM d_icd_diagnoses 
WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( 
    SELECT T4.icd_code 
    FROM ( 
        SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 
        FROM ( 
            SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 
            FROM ( 
                SELECT T1.icd_code, 
                ( 
                    CASE 
                        WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 
                        ELSE 1 
                    END 
                ) as C1 
                FROM ( 
                    SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime 
                    FROM diagnoses_icd 
                    JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id 
                    WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 
                    GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code 
                    HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime 
                ) AS T1 
                JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id 
            ) AS T2 
            GROUP BY T2.icd_code 
        ) AS T3 
    ) AS T4

SELECT T1.drug 
FROM ( 
    SELECT prescriptions.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 
    FROM prescriptions 
    JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id 
    WHERE strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100' 
    AND (CAST((julianday('now') - julianday(admissions.dob))/365.25 AS INTEGER) >= 40 AND CAST((julianday('now') - julianday(admissions.dob))/365.25 AS INTEGER) < 50) 
    GROUP BY prescriptions.drug 
) AS T1 
WHERE T1.C1 <= 5

SELECT T1.drug 
FROM (
    SELECT prescriptions.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 
    FROM prescriptions 
    JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id 
    WHERE strftime('%Y',prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100' 
    AND (julianday(admissions.admittime) - julianday(patients.dob))/365 >= 40 
    AND (julianday(admissions.admittime) - julianday(patients.dob))/365 < 50 
    GROUP BY prescriptions.drug
) AS T1 
WHERE T1.C1 <= 5

SELECT T1.drug 
FROM (
    SELECT prescriptions.drug, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC) AS C1
    FROM prescriptions
    JOIN admissions ON prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id
    JOIN patients ON admissions.subject_id = patients.subject_id
    WHERE patients.age >= 40 AND patients.age < 50
    AND strftime('%Y', prescriptions.starttime) >= '2100'
    GROUP BY prescriptions.drug
) AS T1
WHERE T1.C1 <= 5

FROM (
    SELECT stop_time, start_time, RANK() OVER (ORDER BY DATEDIFF(stop_time, start_time)) AS rnk
    FROM prescriptions
    WHERE drug LIKE '%anesthesia%' AND hadm_id IN (
        SELECT hadm_id 
        FROM admissions 
        WHERE subject_id IN (
            SELECT subject_id 
            FROM patients 
            WHERE diagnosis_icd IN (
                SELECT icd_code 
                FROM d_icd_diagnoses 
                WHERE long_title LIKE '%cancer%'
            )
        )
    )
) AS ranked
WHERE rnk = (SELECT COUNT(*)/2 FROM prescriptions) OR rnk = (SELECT COUNT(*)/2 + 1 FROM prescriptions)

SELECT d_labitems.label 
FROM d_labitems 
WHERE d_labitems.itemid IN 
( 
    SELECT T3.itemid 
    FROM 
    ( 
        SELECT T2.itemid, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC) AS C1 
        FROM 
        ( 
            SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.charttime, admissions.hadm_id 
            FROM diagnoses_icd 
            JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id 
            WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = 
            ( 
                SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code 
                FROM d_icd_diagnoses 
                WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title = 'hyperkalemia' 
            ) 
            AND datetime(diagnoses_icd.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') 
        ) AS T1 
        JOIN 
        ( 
            SELECT admissions.subject_id, labevents.itemid, labevents.charttime, admissions.hadm_id 
            FROM labevents 
            JOIN admissions ON labevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id 
            WHERE datetime(labevents.charttime,'start of year') = datetime(current_time,'start of year','-0 year') 
        ) AS T2 
        ON T1.subject_id = T2.subject_id 
        WHERE T1.charttime < T2.charttime AND T1.hadm_id = T2.hadm_id 
        GROUP BY T2.itemid 
    ) AS T3 
    WHERE T3.C1 <= 3 
)

SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.dose_val_rx, prescriptions.dose_unit_rx 
FROM d_icd_procedures 
JOIN procedures_icd ON d_icd_procedures.icd_code = procedures_icd.icd_code 
JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id 
JOIN prescriptions ON admissions.hadm_id = prescriptions.hadm_id 
WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code = (SELECT icd_code 
                                    FROM (SELECT icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC) AS C1 
                                          FROM procedures_icd 
                                          WHERE datetime(charttime) >= datetime(current_time, '-1 year') 
                                          GROUP BY icd_code) AS T1 
                                    WHERE T1.C1 = 1) 
ORDER BY prescriptions.starttime DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title, prescriptions.drug, prescriptions.dose_val_rx, prescriptions.dose_unit_rx, prescriptions.route 
FROM d_icd_procedures 
JOIN procedures_icd ON d_icd_procedures.icd_code = procedures_icd.icd_code 
JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id 
JOIN prescriptions ON admissions.hadm_id = prescriptions.hadm_id 
WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code = (SELECT icd_code FROM (SELECT icd_code, COUNT(*) AS C1 FROM procedures_icd GROUP BY icd_code ORDER BY C1 DESC LIMIT 1)) 
ORDER BY prescriptions.starttime DESC

FROM prescriptions

    SELECT admissions.hadm_id 
    FROM admissions 
    WHERE admissions.hadm_id = prescriptions.hadm_id 
    ORDER BY admissions.admittime DESC 
    LIMIT 1 
)

    SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title

        SELECT T1.icd_code 
        FROM ( 
            SELECT diagnoses_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 
            FROM diagnoses_icd 
            GROUP BY diagnoses_icd.icd_code 
        ) AS T1 
        WHERE T1.C1 = 1 
    ) 
) 
ORDER BY prescriptions.starttime DESC

        SELECT T1.hadm_id
        FROM (
            SELECT diagnoses_icd.hadm_id, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC) AS C1
            FROM diagnoses_icd

                GROUP BY diagnoses_icd.icd_code
            ) AS T1
            WHERE T1.C1 = 1
        )
    )
)

FROM admissions 
WHERE admissions.admittime >= date('now','-7 days') 
AND admissions.admittime <= date('now') 
AND admissions.hadm_id IN ( 
    SELECT prescriptions.hadm_id 
    FROM prescriptions 
    WHERE prescriptions.starttime = (
        SELECT MIN(prescriptions.starttime) 
        FROM prescriptions 
        WHERE prescriptions.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id 
        GROUP BY prescriptions.hadm_id 
        ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT prescriptions.drug) DESC 
        LIMIT 1 
    ) 
) 
ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC 
LIMIT 1

SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title 
FROM d_icd_diagnoses 
WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN 
( 
    SELECT T4.icd_code 
    FROM 
    ( 
        SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 
        FROM 
        ( 
            SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 
            FROM 
            ( 
                SELECT T1.icd_code, 
                ( CASE 
                    WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',T1.charttime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 
                    ELSE 1 
                END ) as C1 
                FROM 
                ( 
                    SELECT admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code, diagnoses_icd.charttime 
                    FROM diagnoses_icd 
                    JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id 
                    WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',diagnoses_icd.charttime) >= 1 * 365/4 
                    GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code 
                    HAVING MIN(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime 
                ) AS T1 
                JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id 
            ) AS T2 
            GROUP BY T2.icd_code 
        ) AS T3 
    ) AS T4 
    WHERE T4.C3 <= 5 
)

FROM patients 
JOIN admissions ON patients.subject_id = admissions.subject_id 
JOIN procedures_icd ON admissions.hadm_id = procedures_icd.hadm_id 
JOIN d_icd_procedures ON procedures_icd.icd_code = d_icd_procedures.icd_code 
WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN 
( 
    SELECT T1.icd_code 
    FROM

)

SELECT address_city, COUNT(DISTINCT admissions.subject_id) AS patient_count
FROM admissions
JOIN patients ON admissions.subject_id = patients.subject_id
WHERE admissions.hadm_id IN (
    SELECT diagnoses_icd.hadm_id
    FROM diagnoses_icd
    WHERE diagnoses_icd.icd_code = (
        SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code
        FROM d_icd_diagnoses
        WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title LIKE '%hypertension%'
    )
)
GROUP BY address_city
ORDER BY patient_count DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT AVG(microbiologyevents.charttime) as avg_growth_rate_older_than_65, AVG(microbiologyevents.charttime) as avg_growth_rate_younger_than_65 
FROM microbiologyevents 
JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id 
WHERE admissions.dischtime IS NULL 
AND patients.age > 65 
AND patients.age < 65

SELECT AVG(microbiologyevents.value) AS avg_growth_rate, 
CASE 
    WHEN admissions.age > 65 THEN 'older than 65'
    ELSE 'younger than 65'
END AS age_group
FROM microbiologyevents
JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id
WHERE admissions.dischtime IS NULL
GROUP BY age_group

JOIN admissions ON microbiologyevents.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id
WHERE admissions.dischtime IS NULL

SELECT AVG( julianday(admissions.dischtime) - julianday(admissions.admittime) ) AS avg_length_of_stay, patients.smoking_status
FROM admissions
JOIN patients ON admissions.subject_id = patients.subject_id
GROUP BY patients.smoking_status

SELECT AVG(LENGTH_OF_STAY) FROM (SELECT strftime('%J', admissions.dischtime)-strftime('%J', admissions.admittime) AS LENGTH_OF_STAY, patients.subject_id FROM admissions INNER JOIN patients ON admissions.subject_id = patients.subject_id WHERE patients.subject_id IN (SELECT DISTINCT admissions.subject_id FROM admissions INNER JOIN diagnoses_icd ON admissions.hadm_id = diagnoses_icd.hadm_id INNER JOIN d_icd_diagnoses ON diagnoses_icd.icd_code = d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title LIKE '%smoking%' ) GROUP BY patients.subject_id) AS SMOKERS

UNION

INNER JOIN admissions AS completed_admission ON completed_icu_stay.hadm_id = completed_admission.hadm_id
INNER JOIN cost AS completed_cost ON completed_admission.hadm_id = completed_cost.hadm_id
INNER JOIN icustays AS delayed_icu_stay ON completed_cost.hadm_id = delayed_icu_stay.hadm_id

SELECT T5.first_careunit, T5.total_patients, T5.total_deaths, (T5.total_deaths/T5.total_patients) as mortality_rate
FROM (
    SELECT icustays.first_careunit, COUNT(icustays.subject_id) as total_patients, 
    SUM(CASE WHEN patients.dod IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as total_deaths
    FROM icustays
    JOIN patients ON icustays.subject_id = patients.subject_id
    GROUP BY icustays.first_careunit
    ORDER BY mortality_rate DESC
) as T5
LIMIT 1

SELECT physicians.primary_physician FROM physicians WHERE physicians.primary_physician IN (SELECT T3.primary_physician FROM (SELECT T2.primary_physician, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM (SELECT T1.primary_physician, (CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',patients.admittime) < 1 * 365 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) AS C1 FROM patients JOIN admissions ON patients.subject_id = admissions.subject_id GROUP BY patients.primary_physician HAVING MIN(admissions.admittime) = admissions.admittime) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.primary_physician) AS T3 WHERE T3.C2 = (SELECT MAX(C2) FROM (SELECT T2.primary_physician, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM (SELECT T1.primary_physician, (CASE WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',patients.admittime) < 1 * 365 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) AS C1 FROM patients JOIN admissions ON patients.subject_id = admissions.subject_id GROUP BY patients.primary_physician HAVING MIN(admissions.admittime) = admissions.admittime) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id) AS T2))

SELECT primary_physician, AVG(C1) AS mortality_rate
FROM (
    SELECT admissions.subject_id, primary_physician, 
    (CASE 
        WHEN strftime('%J',patients.dod) - strftime('%J',admissions.admittime) < 1 * 365/4 THEN 0 
        ELSE 1 
    END) as C1
    FROM admissions 
    JOIN patients ON admissions.subject_id = patients.subject_id 
    GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, primary_physician
)
GROUP BY primary_physician

SELECT strftime('%Y', admissions.admittime) AS year, COUNT(DISTINCT admissions.hadm_id) AS num_admissions
FROM admissions
JOIN diagnoses_icd ON admissions.hadm_id = diagnoses_icd.hadm_id
JOIN d_icd_diagnoses ON diagnoses_icd.icd_code = d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code
WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title LIKE '%respiratory failure%'
GROUP BY year

SELECT strftime('%Y-%m',admissions.admittime) AS month, COUNT(*) AS num_admissions
FROM admissions
JOIN diagnoses_icd ON admissions.hadm_id = diagnoses_icd.hadm_id
JOIN d_icd_diagnoses ON diagnoses_icd.icd_code = d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code
WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title LIKE '%respiratory failure%'
GROUP BY strftime('%Y-%m',admissions.admittime)
ORDER BY month

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT icustays.stay_id) AS num_admissions, strftime('%Y', admissions.admittime) AS year
FROM admissions
JOIN diagnoses_icd ON admissions.hadm_id = diagnoses_icd.hadm_id
JOIN d_icd_diagnoses ON diagnoses_icd.icd_code = d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code
WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title LIKE '%respiratory failure%'
GROUP BY year

SELECT strftime('%Y',admittime) AS admission_year, COUNT(*) AS admission_count
FROM admissions
WHERE hadm_id IN (
    SELECT hadm_id
    FROM diagnoses_icd
    WHERE icd_code = (
        SELECT icd_code
        FROM d_icd_diagnoses
        WHERE long_title = 'respiratory failure'
    )
)
GROUP BY admission_year
ORDER BY admission_year

SELECT strftime('%Y-%m', admissions.admittime) AS month_year, COUNT(*) AS num_admissions 
FROM admissions 
JOIN diagnoses_icd ON admissions.hadm_id = diagnoses_icd.hadm_id 
JOIN d_icd_diagnoses ON diagnoses_icd.icd_code = d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code 
WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title LIKE '%respiratory failure%' 
GROUP BY month_year 
ORDER BY month_year

SELECT PERCENTILE_CONT(0.5) WITHIN GROUP (ORDER BY admissions.age) AS median_age
FROM admissions
WHERE EXTRACT(MONTH FROM admissions.admittime) = EXTRACT(MONTH FROM CURRENT_DATE)
AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM admissions.admittime) = EXTRACT(YEAR FROM CURRENT_DATE)
AND admissions.age < 18
ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC
LIMIT 1

AND admissions.age < 18
ORDER BY admissions.admittime ASC
LIMIT 1

SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title 
FROM d_icd_procedures 
WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN 
( 
    SELECT T1.icd_code 
    FROM 
    ( 
        SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC ) AS C1 
        FROM procedures_icd 
        WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN 
        ( 
            SELECT admissions.hadm_id 
            FROM admissions 
            WHERE admissions.age > 65 
            AND procedures_icd.careunit = 'Operating Room' 
        ) 
        GROUP BY procedures_icd.icd_code 
    ) AS T1 
)

SELECT d_icd_procedures.long_title
FROM d_icd_procedures
WHERE d_icd_procedures.icd_code IN 
(SELECT procedures_icd.icd_code
FROM procedures_icd
JOIN transfers ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = transfers.hadm_id
WHERE procedures_icd.hadm_id IN 
(SELECT admissions.hadm_id
FROM admissions
WHERE admissions.age > 65)
AND transfers.eventtype = 'transfer'
AND transfers.careunit = 'Operating Room')

SELECT d_items.label, COUNT(*) AS count
FROM d_items
JOIN chartevents ON d_items.itemid = chartevents.itemid
JOIN icustays ON chartevents.stay_id = icustays.stay_id
JOIN transfers ON icustays.hadm_id = transfers.hadm_id
WHERE transfers.careunit = 'medical intensive care unit (micu)' 
AND icustays.first_careunit = 'medical intensive care unit (micu)'
AND d_items.label = 'Operating System'
GROUP BY d_items.label
ORDER BY count DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT d_items.label, COUNT(*) AS count 
FROM admissions 
JOIN icustays ON admissions.hadm_id = icustays.hadm_id 
JOIN transfers ON admissions.hadm_id = transfers.hadm_id 
JOIN d_items ON icustays.first_careunit = transfers.careunit 
WHERE transfers.careunit = 'medical intensive care unit (micu)' 
GROUP BY d_items.label 
ORDER BY count DESC 
LIMIT 1

SELECT d_items.label, COUNT(*) as count
FROM transfers
JOIN admissions ON admissions.hadm_id = transfers.hadm_id
JOIN d_items ON d_items.row_id = transfers.event_id
WHERE transfers.careunit = 'medical intensive care unit (micu)' AND admissions.hadm_id = transfers.hadm_id
GROUP BY d_items.label
ORDER BY count DESC
LIMIT 1

SELECT d_items.label, COUNT(icustays.subject_id) AS count
FROM icustays
JOIN transfers ON icustays.hadm_id = transfers.hadm_id
JOIN d_items ON icustays.first_careunit = d_items.linksto
WHERE transfers.careunit = 'medical intensive care unit (micu)' AND icustays.stay_id = 1
GROUP BY d_items.label
ORDER BY count DESC
LIMIT 1

FROM d_icd_diagnoses 
JOIN diagnoses_icd ON d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code = diagnoses_icd.icd_code 
JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id

GROUP BY d_icd_diagnoses.long_title 
ORDER BY num_icu_stays DESC

SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT icustays.hadm_id FROM icustays WHERE icustays.outtime - icustays.intime > 5 )

SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title, COUNT(*) AS frequency
FROM d_icd_diagnoses
JOIN diagnoses_icd ON d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code = diagnoses_icd.icd_code
JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id
JOIN icustays ON admissions.hadm_id = icustays.hadm_id
WHERE icustays.stay_id IN 
    (SELECT stay_id 
     FROM icustays 
     GROUP BY stay_id 
     HAVING (JulianDay(outtime) - JulianDay(intime)) > 7)
GROUP BY d_icd_diagnoses.long_title
ORDER BY frequency DESC

SELECT d_items.label AS primary_physician, COUNT(DISTINCT admissions.subject_id) AS patient_count 
FROM admissions 
JOIN chartevents ON admissions.hadm_id = chartevents.hadm_id 
JOIN d_items ON chartevents.itemid = d_items.itemid 
WHERE d_items.label = 'primary physician' 
AND admissions.subject_id IN ( 
    SELECT admissions.subject_id 
    FROM admissions 
    JOIN diagnoses_icd ON admissions.hadm_id = diagnoses_icd.hadm_id 
    JOIN d_icd_diagnoses ON diagnoses_icd.icd_code = d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code 
    WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.long_title LIKE '%diabetes%' 
) 
GROUP BY primary_physician 
ORDER BY patient_count DESC 
LIMIT 1

There are several best practices for preventing ICU delirium, including:

1. Implementing protocols for early mobilization and physical therapy to prevent deconditioning and promote cognitive function.
2. Ensuring adequate pain management to prevent agitation and confusion.
3. Minimizing the use of sedatives and ensuring appropriate sedation levels to reduce the risk of delirium.
4. Promoting good sleep hygiene by minimizing noise and disruptions during nighttime hours.
5. Providing orientation cues such as clocks, calendars, and familiar items to help patients maintain a sense of time and place.
6. Involving family members in the care process to provide comfort and support.
7. Monitoring for and addressing any underlying medical conditions or medications that may contribute to delirium.
8. Implementing multidisciplinary team rounds to ensure consistent communication and coordination of care.
9. Educating staff on the signs and symptoms of delirium and the importance of early recognition and intervention.
10. Engaging patients in activities that promote mental stimulation and social interaction.

SELECT AVG(older.procedure_duration - younger.procedure_duration) 
FROM 
(SELECT admissions.hadm_id, 
MAX(procedures_icd.charttime) - MIN(procedures_icd.charttime) AS procedure_duration 
FROM admissions 
JOIN procedures_icd ON admissions.hadm_id = procedures_icd.hadm_id 
WHERE admissions.age < 65 
GROUP BY admissions.hadm_id) AS younger 
JOIN 
(SELECT admissions.hadm_id, 
MAX(procedures_icd.charttime) - MIN(procedures_icd.charttime) AS procedure_duration 
FROM admissions 
JOIN procedures_icd ON admissions.hadm_id = procedures_icd.hadm_id 
WHERE admissions.age >= 65 
GROUP BY admissions.hadm_id) AS older 
ON younger.hadm_id = older.hadm_id

SELECT AVG(older.duration - younger.duration) AS avg_duration_diff
FROM (
    SELECT procedures_icd.hadm_id, SUM(julianday(procedures_icd.charttime) - julianday(icustays.intime)) AS duration
    FROM procedures_icd
    JOIN icustays ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = icustays.hadm_id
    JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id
    WHERE admissions.age >= 65
    GROUP BY procedures_icd.hadm_id
) AS older
JOIN (
    SELECT procedures_icd.hadm_id, SUM(julianday(procedures_icd.charttime) - julianday(icustays.intime)) AS duration
    FROM procedures_icd
    JOIN icustays ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = icustays.hadm_id
    JOIN admissions ON procedures_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id
    WHERE admissions.age < 65
    GROUP BY procedures_icd.hadm_id
) AS younger ON older.hadm_id = younger.hadm_id

SELECT COUNT(admissions.subject_id) as readmissions, transfers.careunit as primary_physician
FROM admissions
JOIN transfers ON admissions.hadm_id = transfers.hadm_id
WHERE transfers.eventtype = 'readmission' AND julianday(transfers.intime) - julianday(admissions.dischtime) <= 30
GROUP BY transfers.careunit
ORDER BY readmissions DESC
LIMIT 1

FROM admissions
JOIN transfers ON admissions.hadm_id = transfers.hadm_id
WHERE transfers.careunit = 'medicine' AND datetime(transfers.intime) BETWEEN date(datetime(admissions.dischtime),'-30 days') AND admissions.dischtime
GROUP BY transfers.first_careunit
ORDER BY readmissions DESC
LIMIT 1

FROM transfers
WHERE transfers.careunit IN (SELECT transfers.careunit FROM transfers WHERE transfers.eventtype = 'discharge' AND datetime(transfers.intime) >= datetime(current_time,'-30 days'))
GROUP BY transfers.careunit
ORDER BY num_readmissions DESC LIMIT 1

SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN (
    SELECT T4.icd_code FROM (
        SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC) AS C3 FROM (
            SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM (
                SELECT T1.icd_code, AVG(strftime('%J',admissions.admittime) - strftime('%J',admissions.dischtime)) AS C1 
                FROM admissions 
                JOIN diagnoses_icd ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id 
                WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',admissions.dischtime) >= 0
                GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, diagnoses_icd.icd_code 
                HAVING MAX(diagnoses_icd.charttime) = diagnoses_icd.charttime
            ) AS T1 
            GROUP BY T1.icd_code
        ) AS T2
    ) AS T3 
    WHERE T3.C3 <= 1 
)

SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN ( SELECT T4.icd_code FROM ( SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER ( ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC ) AS C3 FROM ( SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM ( SELECT T1.icd_code, ( CASE WHEN strftime('%J',admissions.admittime) - strftime('%J',patients.dod) < 1 * 365 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END ) as C1 FROM ( SELECT admissions.subject_id, admissions.hadm_id, admissions.admittime, patients.dod FROM admissions JOIN patients ON admissions.subject_id = patients.subject_id WHERE strftime('%J',current_time) - strftime('%J',admissions.admittime) >= 1 * 365 GROUP BY admissions.subject_id, admissions.hadm_id HAVING MIN(admissions.admittime) = admissions.admittime ) AS T1 JOIN patients ON T1.subject_id = patients.subject_id ) AS T2 GROUP BY T2.icd_code ) AS T3 ) AS T4 WHERE T4.C3 = 1 )

SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title FROM d_icd_diagnoses WHERE d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code IN (
    SELECT T4.icd_code FROM (
        SELECT T3.icd_code, DENSE_RANK() OVER (ORDER BY T3.C2 ASC) AS C3 FROM (
            SELECT T2.icd_code, AVG(C1) AS C2 FROM (
                SELECT T1.icd_code, AVG(strftime('%J',admissions.admittime) - strftime('%J',LAG(admissions.dischtime) OVER (PARTITION BY admissions.subject_id ORDER BY admissions.admittime))) AS C1

    ) AS T4

)

SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title, COUNT(*) AS transfer_count
FROM diagnoses_icd
JOIN d_icd_diagnoses ON diagnoses_icd.icd_code = d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code
JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id
JOIN transfers ON admissions.hadm_id = transfers.hadm_id
WHERE transfers.careunit = 'icu'
GROUP BY d_icd_diagnoses.long_title
ORDER BY transfer_count DESC

FROM d_icd_diagnoses 
JOIN diagnoses_icd ON d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code = diagnoses_icd.icd_code 
JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id 
JOIN transfers ON admissions.hadm_id = transfers.hadm_id 
WHERE transfers.careunit = 'icu' 
GROUP BY d_icd_diagnoses.long_title 
ORDER BY transfer_count DESC

SELECT d_icd_diagnoses.long_title, COUNT(*) as transfer_count 
FROM icustays 
JOIN admissions ON icustays.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id 
JOIN diagnoses_icd ON admissions.hadm_id = diagnoses_icd.hadm_id 
JOIN d_icd_diagnoses ON diagnoses_icd.icd_code = d_icd_diagnoses.icd_code 
GROUP BY d_icd_diagnoses.long_title 
ORDER BY transfer_count DESC 
LIMIT 5

JOIN admissions ON diagnoses_icd.hadm_id = admissions.hadm_id 
JOIN icustays ON admissions.hadm_id = icustays.hadm_id 
GROUP BY d_icd_diagnoses.long_title 
ORDER BY num_transfers DESC
